name: ApartmentPrices
0:
”Alexa, ask Apartment Prices for pricing by city”
”Alexa, ask Apartment Prices for pricing by zip code”
”Alexa, open Apartment Prices”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: apartment prices
des:
This skill provides the latest Zillow median rental price data for studios, one bedroom, and two bedroom apartments by city or zip code. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research.
Hundreds of US cities are included in the data including: New York City, San Francisco California, Seattle Washington, Chicago Illinois, Atlanta Georgia, Portland Oregon, Austin Texas, Phoenix Arizona, Washington D.C., and more! If searching by city, please say the city followed by the state when prompted. (Exception: New York City)
